task.summary:
bugfixes - "mvn clean package" always wants to run a method called "$jacocoInit". This class is not included in our AnnotationsTestClass. Made a workaround, which tests if a methods name is "$jacocoInit". If so, the loop continues with the next method.
- changed what happens when method is not invoceable

Revert "added database credentials"
This reverts commit 2c4cfd7f

added several REST functions: - get - post - delete
todo: put

added rest-func: - put
fixed rest-func: - delete
- fixed web.xml, servlet.xml, beans-bug - added persistence.xml for testing with hsqldb setup - added DBSongListDAOTest
- added xml converter - try to fix connectionpool issue
